mutation ($payload:OAuthCreateClientInput!)

		name
		secret
		authUrl
		redirect
		resourceCodes
		expiredAccessToken
		expiredRefreshToken
		isRevoked
		isMaster
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

graphql.query:
query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	oAuthGetClients (query: $query)
	{
		id
		grantType
		name
		secret
		authUrl
		redirect
		resourceCodes
		expiredAccessToken
		expiredRefreshToken
		isRevoked
		isMaster
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

{
	oAuthFindClient (query: $query)
	{
		id
		grantType
		name
